# Auth Service

Microservice for user authentication and registration in UshaSree Industries.

## Endpoints

- **POST /register** — Register a new user
- **POST /login** — Login with email and password
- **GET /users** — List all users

## Environment Variables

See `.env.example` for required values.

## Docker

```sh
docker build -t <your-dockerhub>/ushasree-auth:latest .
docker run -p 3001:3001 --env-file .env <your-dockerhub>/ushasree-auth:latest
